      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Facebook has shifted its emphasis towards groups since the Facepocalyse of a few years back, and some publishers have been doing good things in them. But they've also become a festering incubator for misinformation and polarisation. I'm sceptical about how much difference this will make, as Facebook is a master at over-promising and under-delivering, but it might impact anyone running group-based communities. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
